text: Private Eyes is the tenth studio album by American duo Hall & Oates and released on 1 September, 1981. It went to number 5 in the United States, number 8 in the United Kingdom and number 9 in New Zealand. ==Track listing== == References == Category:1981 albums Category:Hall & Oates albums Category:RCA Records albums
title: Private Eyes (Hall & Oates album)
